<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="pace-n">pace <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /peɪs/    美 /peɪs/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c">1.★ <strong>[C] 一步：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Walk / Take ten paces forward.
向前走十步。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-u">2.★ <strong>[U] [常用单数] 速度；进度：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He walked <strong>at a fast pace</strong>. 
他疾步行走。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Students study <strong>at their own pace</strong> and the teachers seldom set tests. 
学生按自己的进度学习，老师很少安排考试。</p><footer>北师大⑤ – 15</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>pace of life</strong>
生活节奏</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="keep-pace-with-sb-sth">keep pace (with sb / sth)</h3>
<p>1.<strong>(与某人 / 事物) 并驾齐驱；步调一致</strong>  </p></div>